<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about exec)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/exec.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2018 02:23:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>Python通过配置文件动态修改全局变量</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythontong-guo-pei-zhi-wen-jian-dong-tai-xiu-gai-quan-ju-bian-liang/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;本文学习如何通过配置文件动态修改全局变量。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;看代码main.py：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table class="codetable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos"&gt;&lt;div class="linenodiv"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythontong-guo-pei-zhi-wen-jian-dong-tai-xiu-gai-quan-ju-bian-liang/#rest_code_d93d5a584c494176bcd7807d3e740174-1"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythontong-guo-pei-zhi-wen-jian-dong-tai-xiu-gai-quan-ju-bian-liang/#rest_code_d93d5a584c494176bcd7807d3e740174-2"&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythontong-guo-pei-zhi-wen-jian-dong-tai-xiu-gai-quan-ju-bian-liang/#rest_code_d93d5a584c494176bcd7807d3e740174-3"&gt;3&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythontong-guo-pei-zhi-wen-jian-dong-tai-xiu-gai-quan-ju-bian-liang/#rest_code_d93d5a584c494176bcd7807d3e740174-4"&gt;4&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythontong-guo-pei-zhi-wen-jian-dong-tai-xiu-gai-quan-ju-bian-liang/#rest_code_d93d5a584c494176bcd7807d3e740174-5"&gt;5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;pre class="code python"&gt;&lt;a name="rest_code_d93d5a584c494176bcd7807d3e740174-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="kn"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nn"&gt;conf&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_d93d5a584c494176bcd7807d3e740174-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;conf&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;defaultpath&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_d93d5a584c494176bcd7807d3e740174-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;conf&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;load_conf&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_d93d5a584c494176bcd7807d3e740174-4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"*"&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;50&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_d93d5a584c494176bcd7807d3e740174-5"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;conf&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;defaultpath&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;和代码conf.py：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table class="codetable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos"&gt;&lt;div class="linenodiv"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythontong-guo-pei-zhi-wen-jian-dong-tai-xiu-gai-quan-ju-bian-liang/#rest_code_e18edf28c93a4c0dae0b38a76b4ae9a8-1"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythontong-guo-pei-zhi-wen-jian-dong-tai-xiu-gai-quan-ju-bian-liang/#rest_code_e18edf28c93a4c0dae0b38a76b4ae9a8-2"&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythontong-guo-pei-zhi-wen-jian-dong-tai-xiu-gai-quan-ju-bian-liang/#rest_code_e18edf28c93a4c0dae0b38a76b4ae9a8-3"&gt;3&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythontong-guo-pei-zhi-wen-jian-dong-tai-xiu-gai-quan-ju-bian-liang/#rest_code_e18edf28c93a4c0dae0b38a76b4ae9a8-4"&gt;4&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythontong-guo-pei-zhi-wen-jian-dong-tai-xiu-gai-quan-ju-bian-liang/#rest_code_e18edf28c93a4c0dae0b38a76b4ae9a8-5"&gt;5&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythontong-guo-pei-zhi-wen-jian-dong-tai-xiu-gai-quan-ju-bian-liang/#rest_code_e18edf28c93a4c0dae0b38a76b4ae9a8-6"&gt;6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;pre class="code python"&gt;&lt;a name="rest_code_e18edf28c93a4c0dae0b38a76b4ae9a8-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;defaultpath&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;"/home/long/"&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_e18edf28c93a4c0dae0b38a76b4ae9a8-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_e18edf28c93a4c0dae0b38a76b4ae9a8-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_e18edf28c93a4c0dae0b38a76b4ae9a8-4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;load_conf&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;():&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_e18edf28c93a4c0dae0b38a76b4ae9a8-5"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;span class="n"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;"defaultpath = '/home/long/test'"&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_e18edf28c93a4c0dae0b38a76b4ae9a8-6"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;span class="k"&gt;exec&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="ow"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;globals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(),&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;globals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;运行结果：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; long@happytime:~/exectest$ python main.py
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; /home/long/
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; **************************************************
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; /home/long/test
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;通过load_conf()函数，我们的程序动态修改了全局变量。通过这样的方式就可以实现初始按照默认配置、必要时通过配置文件对全局变量进行修改了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>exec</category><category>Python</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythontong-guo-pei-zhi-wen-jian-dong-tai-xiu-gai-quan-ju-bian-liang/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 09 Sep 2015 02:06:20 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>